  Locus:
    Page: 163
    Verse: 16
Tags:
  - Fault
---
In the degree that we hold a person in the thought of evil or of error, do
we suggest evil and error to him. ...and so in this way we may be sharers
in the very evil-doing in which we hold another in thought.
